</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-71_ pf-text-1"><strong>Action plans</strong> - Develop individual healthcare plans for children with seizure conditions.











</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-73_ pf-text-1"><strong>Awareness</strong> - Promote awareness and understanding among all staff and children about seizures to foster a supportive environment.












